tation-takbeer","tag-glorification-tasbeeh","tag-good-deeds-hasanat","tag-graves","tag-hereafter-akhirah","tag-manners-adab","tag-remembrance-al-dhikr","tag-supplication-al-dua"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9fD","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":24471,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/03\/05\/dua-takbir-tasbih-before-asking\/","url_meta":{"origin":35565,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Exalt, glorify, praise Allah before asking","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: Umm Sulaym came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and she said, \u201cTeach me some words to say in my prayer.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cExalt Allah ten times, glorify Allah ten times, praise Allah ten times, then ask for whatever you wish. Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17537,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/09\/tasbih-tahmid-33-times\/","url_meta":{"origin":35565,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Glorify Allah 33 times after every prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 9, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The poor emigrants came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, saying, \u201cThe wealthy have taken the highest degrees and blessed ranks!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHow is that?\u201d They said, \u201cThey pray as we pray, they fast as we fast, they give in\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38373,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/10\/24\/dhikr-shaytan-distracts\/","url_meta":{"origin":35565,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Easy way to Paradise, but Satan distracts them","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 24, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere are two practices no Muslim man preserves but that he will enter Paradise. Surely, they are both easy yet few act upon them. Glorify Allah at the end of every prayer ten times, praise\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36341,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/25\/long-life-tasbih-takbir-tahlil\/","url_meta":{"origin":35565,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Life: Best believers live long to glorify Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 25, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Talhah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no one better to Allah than a believer who lives long to glorify Him, exalt Him, and declare His oneness.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 1401 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0637\u064e\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0629 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15483,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/29\/dua-prophet-travelers\/","url_meta":{"origin":35565,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet supplicates for travelers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I intend to travel, so instruct me.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou must be mindful of Allah and exalt Him every time you ascend a height.\u201d As the man turned to leave, the Prophet said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32274,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/18\/doors-of-khayr-plentiful\/","url_meta":{"origin":35565,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Doors of virtuous good deeds are plentiful","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no soul in the son of Adam but that charity is due upon it on every day the sun rises.\u201d It was said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, from what can we give in charity?\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp